==Arabic==
===Etymology===
Made up of the preposition {{ARchar|[[ب#Preposition|ب]]}} (bi-) , "in, with", + the definite article {{ARchar|[[ال]]}} (al-) + the verbal noun from the verb {{ARchar|[[كاد]]}} (kāda), "to be on the point".

===Adverb===
'''{{ARchar|بالكاد}}''' (b-il-kād)

# [[almost]], [[nearly]]
# [[merely]]

